title: Infowars Attacks Ethan - H3 Podcast # 243
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast Ethan assembles the foot soldiers once again to take on the haters- this time the goons at Infowars! Also Usher is issuing his own currency and tipping people with it, and Dan & Zach have an epic Rock Trivia showdown!
